description: If you’ve ever been to any of the fun festivals, fairs, or fundraising events in Phoenix, you’re probably familiar with Southwest Kettle Corn - the custom mobile trailer where you find the best kettle corn, as well as a cornucopia of creative gourmet flavors; caramel, cheddar, cinnamon sugar, fruity, and other favorites. So the next time any of you Phoenicians are looking to feast on popcorn of optimal quality, you gotta have Southwest Kettle Corn pop on by.
name: Southwest Kettle Corn
